Privacy Policy

Your privacy is important to us. It is our policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect.

Information We Collect

We collect the following personal information from our users:
- Name
- Email Address
- Phone Number
- Location

How We Use Your Information

The personal information we collect is primarily used for the following purposes:
- Account Creation: To create and manage your user account.
- Improving User Experience: To enhance and personalize your experience on our platform.
- Data Sharing:

Currently, your personal information is not shared with any third parties. However, in the future, there may be circumstances where sharing your data becomes necessary. This could be for improving the user experience or enhancing our platform. Rest assured, any such sharing will be done with utmost care and consideration for your privacy and safety.

Accessing Information

You have full control over your personal information. You can access and update your details directly through the app. If you encounter any issues or need assistance, you can also contact our support team.

